<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1041960' id='t-1041960'>The more I play, the happier I am,
and the happier my kids are.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1045920' id='t-1045920'>The more I play,
the more I feel like a good mother.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1049200' id='t-1049200'>The more I play,
the freer my mind becomes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1051680' id='t-1051680'>The more I play, the better I work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1053600' id='t-1053600'>The more I play, the more I feel the hum,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1056120' id='t-1056120'>the nation I'm building,
the marathon I'm running,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1058520' id='t-1058520'>the troops, the canvas,
