<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1061164' id='t-1061164'>the other hum, the real hum,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1064000' id='t-1064000'>life's hum.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1065480' id='t-1065480'>The more I feel that hum,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1066760' id='t-1066760'>the more this strange,
