<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1070320' id='t-1070320'>awkward, brand new,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1071680' id='t-1071680'>alive non-titan feels like me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1075120' id='t-1075120'>The more I feel that hum,
