</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1091840' id='t-1091840'>I said yes to less work and more play.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1095680' id='t-1095680'>Titans need not apply.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1098160' id='t-1098160'>Wanna play?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1099960' id='t-1099960'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
